data.name: Zesty Pickle Salad
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing and tangy salad that adds a delightful crunch to your meal.
detailedCookingInstructions: In a large bowl, combine chopped pickles, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, red onion, and fresh parsley.
In a separate small bowl, whisk together olive oil, apple cider vinegar, salt, pepper, and garlic powder.
Pour the dressing over the salad and toss gently to combine.
Serve immediately or refrigerate for a few minutes to enhance the flavors.
data.modifiersForBase: Adding fresh vegetables and a tangy dressing
